snippet.title: Egghead Gumpty - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam Link:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2067570/Egghead_Gumpty/

A horror game where you explore an infinite procedurally-generated abandoned juvie as you try to survive a monstrous egg with legs named Egghead Gumpty.
